<inglise> - financing of studies, seminars and fora for the exchange of experience in the above fields. </inglise>
<eesti> - uuringute, seminaride ja foorumite rahastamine, mis v&otilde;imaldavad vahetada kogemusi eespool nimetatud valdkondades. </eesti>
<inglise> Particular attention shall be paid to the participation of local people and target groups in identifying, planning and carrying out operations. </inglise>
<eesti> Erilist t&auml;helepanu p&ouml;&ouml;ratakse kohalike elanike ning sihtgruppide osalemisele ettev&otilde;tmiste kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramisel, kavandamisel ja elluviimisel. </eesti>
<inglise> The Community shall only finance projects in which respect for human rights is guaranteed. </inglise>
