<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The instruments to be employed in the course of the operations referred to in Articles 3 and 4 shall include studies, technical assistance, training or other services, supplies and works, along with audits and evaluation and monitoring missions. </inglise>
